subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Top-ranked Roger Federer had to work a little harder than expected before beating Victor Hanescu of Romania, 6-3, 6-7 (5), 6-1, in the second round of the BNP Paribas Open in Indian Wells, Calif.
